---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Travel" description="Getting to Jack and Jenna's wedding: airports, hotels, and parking near Santa Barbara.">

  <div class="section section--wide">
    <h1 class="page-heading">Travel</h1>
    <p class="page-intro prose">
      For anyone coming from out of town &mdash; here's everything you need to plan your trip.
    </p>

    <div class="travel-blocks">

      <section class="travel-section">
        <h2 class="display travel-heading">Getting Here</h2>
        <div class="airport-grid">
          <div class="airport">
            <h3 class="airport-code display">SBA</h3>
            <p class="airport-name">Santa Barbara Airport</p>
            <p>
              Closest option. Served by United, American, and Alaska from major hubs.
              About 20 minutes to most venues in the area.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="airport">
            <h3 class="airport-code display">LAX</h3>
            <p class="airport-name">Los Angeles International</p>
            <p>
              More routes and usually cheaper flights. 90&ndash;120 minutes to Santa Barbara
              depending on traffic. Rent a car or take the Amtrak Pacific Surfliner.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="travel-tip">
          The Amtrak Pacific Surfliner runs from LA Union Station directly to Santa Barbara.
          Comfortable, scenic, and avoids the 101 entirely.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <section class="travel-section">
        <h2 class="display travel-heading">Where to Stay</h2>
        <div class="hotel-placeholder">
          <p class="display hotel-soon">Hotel block coming soon</p>
          <p>
            We're working on securing a room block at a nearby hotel. Once confirmed,
            the details and booking link will appear here. In the meantime, here are
            a few areas worth looking at:
          </p>
          <ul class="area-list">
            <li><strong>Goleta</strong> &mdash; closest to the Bacara / Haskell's Beach area, many hotel options</li>
            <li><strong>Downtown Santa Barbara</strong> &mdash; walkable, great restaurants, 15&ndash;20 min to most venues</li>
            <li><strong>Camarillo</strong> &mdash; if the venue is on that end, more affordable chains</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <section class="travel-section">
        <h2 class="display travel-heading">Parking</h2>
        <p>
          [Parking details to be confirmed with venue. Note will be added here once
          logistics are locked in &mdash; including whether there's on-site parking,
          overflow options, or a shuttle from a nearby lot.]
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're planning to drink at the reception, we'd encourage using a rideshare.
          Uber and Lyft are available throughout the Santa Barbara area.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-intro {
  margin-bottom: var(--s-lg);
  color: oklch(from var(--charcoal) calc(l + 0.25) c h);
}

.travel-blocks {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s-lg);
}

.travel-section {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s-sm);
}

.travel-heading {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.airport-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: var(--s-md);
  margin-block: var(--s-sm);
}

.airport {
  padding: var(--s-md);
  border: 1px solid oklch(from var(--blush) l c h / 0.45);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.airport-code {
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  line-height: 1;
}

.airport-name {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.travel-tip {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: oklch(from var(--charcoal) calc(l + 0.25) c h);
  padding: var(--s-sm) var(--s-md);
  border-left: none;
  background: oklch(from var(--sage) l c h / 0.1);
  border: 1px solid oklch(from var(--sage) l c h / 0.3);
}

.hotel-placeholder {
  padding: var(--s-md);
  border: 1px solid oklch(from var(--blush) l c h / 0.4);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s-sm);
}

.hotel-soon {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.area-list {
  padding-left: 1.2rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}
.area-list li { line-height: 1.5; }

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .airport-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
